modName: Legend of Zelda- Fierce Deity Sword
summary: My 3rd Sword mod for Skyrim and my 3rd legend of zelda sword.
descriptionHtml:
Modeled in Maya 2012 and textured in mudbox and photoshop. This is my 3rd sword and i  tried to improve texturing a bit from my other sword, tell me what you think about this sword.

Time spent:
Modeling: 3hours
Texturing: 1hour
Total: about 4hours

Didnt model and texture for a straight 4hours took breaks inbetween so its an estimation based on when i saved the completed model and the textures

*i noticed i added an s to deity, dont know why but whatever.*
author: EpicSenseney
